HEADWORD: Intertie
<hw>In"ter*tie`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Arch.)</fld>
<def>In any framed work, a horizontal tie other than sill and plate or
other principal ties, securing uprights to one another.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

